<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta http-equiv="x-ua-compatible" content="ie=edge">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">
<title>403 Forbidden</title>
<style>
body {
color: #000;
font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
margin: 5px auto;
max-width: 1000px;
width: 96%;
background-color: beige;
}
.page {
display: flex;
justify-content: center;
align-items: center;
padding: 20px;
}
.main {
border: 10px solid white;
background-color: antiquewhite;
box-shadow: 0 0 4px black;
padding: 20px;
padding-bottom: 30px;
border-radius: 10px;
}
h1, h2 {
margin: auto;
padding: 10px 0;
}
.error-code {
color: #f47755;
font-size: 40px;
font-weight: bold;
line-height: 1;
}
.txtC {
text-align: center;
}
.actions {
margin-top: 26px;
}
.actions a {
border: 2px solid #23a7de;
padding: 8px 16px;
text-decoration: none;
}
.actions a:hover {
text-decoration: none;
background: #23a7de;
color: #fff;
}
.rtl {
direction: rtl;
}
p.lead {
font-size: 16px;
color: #4f5a64;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="page">
<div class="main">
<h1 class="txtC">Server Error</h1>
<div class="error-code txtC">403</div>
<h2 class="txtC">Forbidden</h2>
<p class="lead">You do not have permission to access this document.</p>
<hr/>
<p class="rtl txtC">شما به این قسمت دسترسی ندارید.</p>
<div class="actions txtC">
<a href="/">انجمن لوتی</a>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>